.TH nbd-cli 8
.SH NAME
.B nbd-cli
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B nbd-cli
is a cli utility, which aims at making backstore creation/deletion/mapping/unmaping/listing.

.SH SYNOPSIS
.B nbd-cli [OPTION] [COMMAND [OPTIONS]]

.SH NBD-CLI OPTIONS

.TP
